---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Date Night Pottery Painting"
  description="Romantic pottery painting experience for couples in Centerville, TN. Create beautiful pieces together while bonding."
  price="$25-35 per couple"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="date night pottery, couples activity, romantic date, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Date Night Pottery Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Looking for a unique, romantic date experience? Paint beautiful pottery pieces together in our intimate, couple-focused setting. Create lasting memories and keepsakes of your time together.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is pottery painting designed specifically for couples. You'll select pre-made pieces—whether matching designs or complementary pieces—and paint them together. Our romantic setting and expert guidance make this the perfect date activity.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Two pottery pieces to select and paint</li>
      <li>All painting supplies and paints</li>
      <li>Expert guidance and instruction</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Romantic, couple-focused atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home keepsakes of your date</li>
      <li>Option: Café refreshments available</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Date nights looking for something unique</li>
      <li>Anniversary celebrations</li>
      <li>Special occasions</li>
      <li>Couples wanting quality time together</li>
      <li>Anyone seeking romantic creative bonding</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and romantic setting (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Select your pottery pieces (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint together with guidance (60-75 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches and photos (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take-home your keepsakes</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per couple<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your romantic date!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best date night we've had in years! Creating pottery together was so fun and romantic. We love our pieces!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>John & Lisa</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"For our anniversary, we wanted something special. This was perfect—romantic, creative, and memorable!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Mike & Jennifer</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Worth the drive from Franklin! We have pieces we made together that remind us of this wonderful date!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Brad & Angela</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Date Night Candle Making</h3>
        <p>Create custom candles together for a romantic evening.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/date-night-candle-making" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Adult Pottery Painting Night</h3>
        <p>Adults-only pottery painting for a fun evening out.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/adult-pottery-painting-night" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint and Pour Pottery Candle</h3>
        <p>Combine pottery painting with candle making for double the creativity.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/paint-and-pour-pottery-candle" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
